title: The Legends 55+ Apartments: Luxury Meets Affordability. 2 BR Available
posting_body: ['At The Legends of Spring Lake Park, our independent living community captures the essence of living well.', 'Enjoy the comforts of maintenance-free living along with the convenience of an outstanding location!', 'These incredible 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment homes offer quality features such as granite kitchen counter-tops, spacious 9’ ceilings, and even a full-size, in-home washer & dryer.', 'The Legends also provides a wealth of community amenities for you and your new neighbors to enjoy, including a beauty salon, 24-hour fitness center, card & crafts room, theater room and community room with full kitchen and a cozy fireplace.', 'Reserve your new home today before they’re gone!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Outdoor Patio & Grilling Areas', '- 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Service', '- Over-Sized Windows Provide Tons of Natural Sunlight', '- 24-Hour Fitness Center', '- 55+ Active Living Community!', '- Water, Sewer & Trash Removal Services', 'Included', '- Open & Spacious Floorplans', '- Kitchen Breakfast Bar or Island', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Spring Lake Park is an active 55+ living community that participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Spring Lake Park', '1066 County Highway 10 NE', 'Spring Lake Park, MN, 55432', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '8c5xmtkK']
